# Setup Apache Maven on Windows

- For setting-up apache maven on windows11, kindly follow this official download link: https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi

## 01. Download and Configure Maven on Win 11

- Navigate to https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi and download the [Binary zip archive](https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.9/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.9-bin.zip) file.

- Unzip the downloaded **apache-maven-3.9.9-bin.zip** file and extract it in **C:\Binaries** folder

## 02. Setting-up home path for Maven

- **M2** = C:\Binaries\apache-maven-3.9.9\bin
- **M2_HOME** = %M2%\apache-maven-3.9.9
- PATH = C:\Binaries\apache-maven-3.9.9\bin
